reviewText: I liked the dvd but found that some of the episodes the color and the audio was bad. Did anyone else have this problem?

Great cartoons for kids. mine loved them. I had them on VHS,but you can't find a player for them. I want my grand kids to enjoy them. I never sent for anythhing on my own, but when I saw these, on Amazon I learned fast. Thanks for such fast delivery...I know my 2 little ones will love these as much as their moms...
